<lb n="19" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">haṇādraṅgēndram giri</hi>
<lb n="20" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">maindranīlamakarō<unclear>ddha</unclear>nya<unclear>ḥ</unclear></hi>
