<lb n="37" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">taiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> śayyāvēśma bhujaṅ</hi>
<lb n="38" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">garājaśayanadvāram vitā</hi>
